import React from 'react'
import { WhitePortfolioContainer, RedHeaderBox, FeatureDesktopBigBox, FeatureContainer, FeatureCard, FeatureTextContainer } from '../lib/container'
import { BoxHeader, TechBoxText, RedHeader, FeatureText } from '../lib/text'
import { FeatureImage } from '../lib/image'

export const Thoughts = () => {
  return (
    <WhitePortfolioContainer>
      <RedHeaderBox>
        <BoxHeader>MY THOUGHTS</BoxHeader>
      </RedHeaderBox>
      <FeatureImage
        href='https://medium.com/@jihyunan42/dear-diary-i-learned-how-to-toggle-display-in-react-today-44f9c5b4fa91'
        alt='screenshot of blog post'
        mobileUrl={require(`../images/thoughts-mobile-toggle.jpg`)}
        desktopUrl={require(`../images/thoughts-2-desktop.jpg`)}
      />
      <FeatureTextContainer>
        <RedHeader>JUL 2020</RedHeader>
        <FeatureText>Fantastic 24 weeks of coding in retrospective.</FeatureText>
        <FeatureText>This spring I made a leap into the world of unknown, that is the world of code.
        I started from knowing virtually nothing about code and the following 24 weeks of learning code was,
        well, a bit of a rollercoaster ride.
        </FeatureText>
      </FeatureTextContainer>
    </WhitePortfolioContainer>
  )
}

export default Thoughts
